imdb.plot outline: "Down to Business" is a new TV/media series currently being produced by Random Original at our studio in Everett, Washington. The show focuses on providing in-depth coverage on marketing and advertising, which impacts businesses from one-man bands to Fortune 500 companies. Host Josh Dirks sits down with business owners from Seattle and surrounding areas to talk about who they are, what they do, and how they manage their marketing and advertising for their businesses. Through the show we work to check current marketing trends, review past successes and failures, and sit down with a variety of business owners to audit their current and past marketing strategies and tactics, pointing out what has been working and some possible areas for improvement to provide a higher return on investment of their marketing dollars.
